BioCirV - Materialized Views Specification for MVP

Date: 2026-02-23
From: Web App Engineering Team
To: Data Team
Status: Draft - awaiting data team review
Context

The BioCirV web app reads biomass data from your PostgreSQL database in read-only mode. We need 9 materialized views that flatten and pre-aggregate data into the shapes our frontend pages consume. You own the view definitions and refresh schedule; we just SELECT from them.
This document defines the expected columns and data shape for each view, mapped directly to the prototype UI.
